ister.go`)** | MISSING | No scheme registration |\n| **Fake clients (`typed/.../fake/`)** | MISSING | No fake subdirectory; single `fake.go` at clientset root |\n| **Fake clientset (`clientset/versioned/fake/`)** | MISSING | No fake clientset directory |\n| **`doc.go` markers** | MISSING | None exist anywhere in client-go |\n| **Informers: per-type (`agentruntime.go`, `codeinterpreter.go`)** | MISSING | Only stub implementations in `v1alpha1/interface.go` |\n| **Informers: `generic.go` (`ForResource`)** | MISSING | No generic resource routing |\n| **Informers: `internalinterfaces/factory_interfaces.go`** | MISSING | No `NewInformerFunc`, `TweakListOptionsFunc` |\n| **Informers: `SharedInformerFactory` full interface** | PARTIAL | Missing `WaitForCacheSync` return type mismatch (`map[string]bool` vs `map[reflect.Type]bool`), missing `ForResource`, `InformerFor`, constructors with options |\n| **Listers: individual files (`agentruntime.go`, `codeinterpreter.go`)** | PARTIAL | All lister code is in `expansion_generated.go` instead of separate files |\n| **Listers: `AgentRuntimeListerExpansion` / `NamespaceListerExpansion`** | MISSING | No expansion interfaces on listers |\n| **`make gen-client` / `hack/update-codegen.sh`** | UNKNOWN | No Makefile target or hack script found |\n\n### Summary\n\n**Compliance: ~25%** â€” The implementation is a simplified in-memory stub that covers the basic interface shapes for `AgentRuntimeInterface` and `CodeInterpreterInterface` (minus `DeleteCollection` and expansion hooks), but is missing the vast majority of the spec: proper directory layout, discovery client, REST client, scheme registration, fake clients, full informer factory, per-type informer/lister files, code generation infrastructure, and all tests.","time":{"start":1775843328875,"end":1775843328875}}}
